<p>Our BEANS! idyllic beach-front hostel has been serving volunteers and travelers for ten years. We combine <a href="accommodation-and-food.html" title="Find out more about the accommodation and food we offer">low-impact, natural living</a> with <a href="community-projects.html" title="Find out more about our community projects">projects that actively benefit the village</a>.</p>

