<p>Whether you are looking to escape, contemplate and create, <a href="activities-and-excursions.html#surfing" title="Find out more about our surfing services">surf</a>, or just unwind for a few days, you will appreciate authentic Nicaraguan life at the beautiful beach setting of <a href="about-jiquilillo.html" title="Find out more about Jiquilillo">Jiquilillo</a> where you'll be confident that your presence is doing good not harm.</p>

<p>If you want a new perspective, our <a href="community-projects.html" title="Find out how to become a volunteer with us">volunteer opportunities</a> give you a chance to get involved in our community projects. We offer <a href="activities-and-excursions.html#surfing" title="Find out more about our surfing services">surf rentals and surf lessons</a>, and also provide board repair. The local kids within <a href="community-projects.html#surf-club" title="Find out more about our Surf Club project">Surf Club</a> can provide their knowledge of local beach breaks, including the nearby shore and point breaks of El Asserradores.</p>

<p>For the adventurous, <a href="activities-and-excursions.html" title="Find out more about our community-based tours">we and the community offer</a> kayaking, volcano hikes, horse back riding, and <a href="activities-and-excursions.html#cultural-excursions" title="Find out more about our cultural excursions">cultural excursions</a>.</p>

